// hazard curve -- was built and never called from anywhere since. When ON, an open trade is closed
// once its own regime's bucketed favourable-run hazard rate clears the threshold at its current
// holding duration (in bars, approximated from holdingMinutes/Period() -- an honest approximation,
// not a claim of exact bar-count tracking per trade). Same risk tier as WARRANT#84/28 -- closing a
// trade is a live-decision change. WARRANT#90 (2026-07-22): activated per Manuel's go-ahead.
